title: PicturesToExe Deluxe 9.0.18 Full With Medicine[BabuPC]
description:
Create professional slideshows in PicturesToExe. Add photos, video clips, & music. Output for PC, Mac, DVD, HD video, & YouTube.

For Enthusiasts and Professionals
PicturesToExe is available in two editions — Essentials and Deluxe. You can choose the right product for you. Compare editions.

Images and Video Clips
Put images, videos, and text objects on a slide.
Mix objects together on the screen.

Slide Styles and Transitions
120+ customizable slide styles and transition effects.
Infinite number of unique styles. Create new styles and transitions.

Keyframe Animation
Adjust pan, zoom, rotate, 3D transformations.
Control opacity, blur, unsharp mask, and color effects.

Hierarchical Animation
Create complex parent-child animation of objects.

Masks
Apply masking effect to a group of objects.

Audio Tracks
Add and view multiple audio tracks which may be played simultaneously.
Synchronize slides with audio clips on the timeline using time points.
Link audio clips with slides
